19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
20
21 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code § 3-4-609 is amended to read as follows:
22 3-4-609. Wholesaler permit — Issuance — Transfer.
23 (a)(1)(a) A new wholesaler permit shall not be issued under § 3-4-605
24 or § 3-4-607 on or after September 1, 2013 may be issued on or after July 1,
25 2026.
26 (b) A new minimum wholesaler permit under § 3-4-607 may be issued on
27 or after the effective date of this act.
28 (2) However, a holder of a wholesaler permit under § 3-4-605 or
29 § 3-4-607 issued on or before September 1, 2013, may renew the permit before,
30 on, or after September 1, 2013.
31 (b) A holder of a wholesaler permit issued under § 3-4-605 or § 3-4-
32 607 on or before September 1, 2013, may transfer the wholesaler permit to
33 another wholesaler as permitted under applicable law or regulation of the
34 Alcoholic Beverage Control Division.
